{"tid":1889953,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（吹大雞）請大家稅局舉報藍絲Youtube暪稅","createTime":"2020-02-21T01:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T07:47:06.000Z","uid":72431,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"07d9b774ed16af5635e660bdd42837f18877c8e7","tid":1889953,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:50:52.000Z","msg":"講多次<br />\nYouTube 紅底你舉報完，佢聽日上訴就開番，反而你po佢條link會幫佢宣傳，刷view,你睇下西門敬就知，我本身唔識佢比你地日po夜po搞到我識左，佢youtube被ban左一陣，上訴，聽日就開番，舉報根本就無用<br />\n<br />\n請大家send email舉報佢地暪稅仲好<br />\nYouTube 有分紅，佢地收人科金，你估佢地有報稅咩<br />\n記住要搞就要現實搞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去下面個網到download form，send email搞掂<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.irs.gov/zh-hant/individuals/how-do-you-report-suspected-tax-fraud-activity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fzh-hant%2Findividuals%2Fhow-do-you-report-suspected-tax-fraud-activity&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=22dc608e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.irs.gov/zh-hant/individuals/how-do-you-report-suspected-tax-fraud-activity</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，我仲諗緊有咩渠道可以舉報，1823，公司商業登記處，1823？？？大家幫手諗諗"},{"pid":"85e9325a0bfc1c588b9e4b6659580f925d8ba66e","tid":1889953,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:28:42.000Z","msg":"Go"},{"pid":"b049f74ddc69f950523c28ccbadcb977d0eedc0d","tid":1889953,"uid":14494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:29:13.000Z","msg":"小心回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42fde782ef6fa20d74325202593fe33bf839ff1","tid":1889953,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"421f664b6bb6f831d721c0aae3bc50ceb1414446","tid":1889953,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:08:13.000Z","msg":"[Youtube第一波攻勢] 召集所有手足：集中Twitter洗板，我要所有執行政治